text: Philippe Vitel (born February 22, 1955 in Toulon) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Var department, and is a member of the Union for a Popular Movement. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:People from Toulon Category:Union for a Popular Movement politicians Category:The Popular Right Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
title: Philippe Vitel
